		<header>
			
			<h1>Corporate restructuring in the EU sugar sector: Implications for the ACP</h1>

						<div class="pdf-file">
				<a href="/en/layout/set/print/content/download/7399/178475/file/0530130fc92d4fff0f92cb4f80947d3c.pdf">Download <img src="/extension/agritrade/design/agritrade/images/pdf.gif" alt="" /></a>
			</div>
			
			<h4>
												30 April 2010
										</h4>

						<h2>May 2010</h2>
					</header>


				<div class="intro">

						<a name="eztoc178463_2" id="eztoc178463_2"></a><h2>Contents</h2><p>

<a href="#1" target="_self">1 Introduction</a><br />

<a href="#2" target="_self">2 Changing corporate ownership and alliances and their potential policy...</a><br />

<a href="#2" target="_self">2.1 Expansion of Associated British Foods (ABF)</a><br />

