<a href="#25" target="_self">2.5 Nordzucker’s pan-European alliance</a><br />

<a href="#26" target="_self">2.6 Smaller players link up</a><br />

<a href="#27" target="_self">2.7 Implications for EU policies impacting on the sugar sector</a><br />

<a href="#3" target="_self">3 Implications for the ACP</a><br />

<a href="#31" target="_self">3.1 Short-term insulation</a><br />

<a href="#32" target="_self">3.2 The functioning of the ACP-EU sugar supply chain</a><br />

